title: AXL-DC - Bon's Tracks 2016 ak
description:
AXL-DC - Bon's Tracks 2016 ak

Well I have heard from some and seen signs that the interest is there even though the sound is less than top notch. But With Bon Tracks Hell even Brian never had them down as my first choice. The Bon tracks are compatible with Axl's style As I have been lstening to this for a bit now. And according to Blabbermouth and others they are going to write material and are planning a tour geared up to the AXL-DC Line up.

01. Sin City.mp3
02. Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap.mp3
03. Shot Down to in Flames.mp3

09. If You Want Blood (You've Got It).mp3
10. Hell Ain't a Bad Place to Be.mp3
11. Whole Lotta Rosie.mp3
12. Riff Raff.mp3



Its rough and mean it's mighty unclean but its gonna be the future of This band if all the noises are on track. But it's still Axl we dealing with and so anything could happen.
